snippet.title: Orch Star - Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Store Page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/727100/Orch_Star/
This video is outdated. Watch the updated trailer here: https://youtu.be/w5cnnoyd0SE

Orch Star is a real time strategy game set in an immersive space universe where orchs, elves, dwarves and humans fight for domination. The game can be played on Windows desktop, HTC Vive and Oculus Rift, and will be released on Steam Early Access Dec 14th.
